---
/**
 * Vertical numbered timeline used for step-by-step processes inside MDX.
 * Wraps a sequence of <Step> children. Numbering is automatic via a CSS
 * counter on the <ol>, so authors don't pass `n=`.
 *
 * Visual / structural rules live in src/styles/global.css under the
 * `.mdx-body .iteration-cycle` block (kept there with the other prose
 * styles so timeline behaviour can't drift from the surrounding
 * typography rhythm).
 */
---

<ol class="iteration-cycle">
  <slot />
</ol>
